     C  N30                Z-ADD*YEAR     M6SYY
     C  N30                Z-ADDUMONTH    M6SMM
     C  N30                Z-ADDUDAY      M6SDD
     C  N30                Z-ADD01        M6SBN
      **５０**
     C           M6STI1    IFEQ 50
     C************         MOVE *BLANK    M6DKTO
     C************         MOVE 'Y'       M6KPUT
     C                     ELSE
      **６３**
     C           M6STI1    IFEQ 63
     C                     ELSE
      **以外**
     C           M6KRU2    IFNE 'Z'
