     CSR         ESB711    ENDSR
      *---------------------------*
      * A-PICS 以外　調整枚数
      *---------------------------*
     CSR         #SB720    BEGSR
      *
     C                     Z-ADD0         SA@     50
      *今回ー前回　枚数
     C           WMAIS     SUB  SVKMAX    SA      50
     C                     Z-ADDSA        SA@
     C                     MULT -1        SA@
      *今回/前回
     C                     Z-ADD0         RITU    72
     C           SVKMAX    IFNE 0
     C           WMAIS     DIV  SVKMAX    RITU
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     MULT 100       RITU
     C           RITU      IFGE 100
     C                     SUB  100       RITU
     C                     ELSE
     C           100       SUB  RITU      RITU
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           RITU      IFLT WKADJU
     C                     Z-ADDSA@       M6AUAJ
     C                     ADD  M6AUAJ    M6CMAI
